decision_details:
- on a proposal made by the Minister of Education, Hon. Bandula Gunawardena, Cabinet approval was granted to entrust the incomplete construction work of the following schools, to the State Owned Central Engineering Consultancy Bureau (CECB) to be completed in 2011:
* Sujatha Girls' School, Kandy; 
* Sujatha Girls' (Vidyawardhena) Vidyalaya, Colombo; 
* Ratnawali Girls' School, Gampaha; 
* Sujatha Girls' School, Matara; 
* Anula Vidyalaya, Nugegoda; 
* Siri Piyarathane Vidyalaya, Padukka; and 
* Devi Balika Vidyalaa, Colombo.
